lass_list":["post-4031","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-quran-exegesis-tafsir","tag-abu-bakr","tag-battle-of-uhud","tag-bounty-naeem","tag-dates-al-tamr","tag-day-of-resurrection","tag-debt-al-dayn","tag-food-al-taam","tag-gratitude-al-shukr","tag-hereafter-akhirah","tag-jews-yahud","tag-martyrs-shuhada","tag-people-of-the-book-ahl-kitab","tag-prophetic-biography-seerah-nabawiyya","tag-surah-al-takathur","tag-trade-al-tijarah","tag-trees","tag-water-al-maa"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-131","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":34420,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/09\/30\/uhud-trembles-khulafa\/","url_meta":{"origin":4031,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Caliphs: Uhud trembles for Abu Bakr, Umar, and Uthman","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 30, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, was climbing Mount Uhud with Abu Bakr, Umar, and Uthman when it began to quake because of them. The Prophet said, \u201cBe still, Uhud! It is but a Prophet, a truthful man, and two martyrs upon you!\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34484,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/10\/20\/sadaqah-allah-multiplies-uhud\/","url_meta":{"origin":4031,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Sadaqah: Allah multiplies charity until it is like a mountain","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 20, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah will raise up a date or a morsel in charity, just as one of you raises his mare or his young, until it becomes like the mountain of Uhud.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn H\u0323ibba\u0304n 3317 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":22712,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/04\/23\/prophet-forgives-battle-uhud\/","url_meta":{"origin":4031,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Jihad: The Prophet asks Allah to forgive them at Uhud","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 23, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Sahl ibn Sa\u2019d reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cO Allah, forgive my people for they do not know.\u201d Abu Hatim said, \u201cThe Prophet said this supplication during the battle of Uhud when they slashed his face.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn H\u0323ibba\u0304n 973 Grade: Hasan\u00a0(fair)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6819,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/21\/umar-competes-with-abu-bakr\/","url_meta":{"origin":4031,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Competition: Umar tries to compete with Abu Bakr","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 21, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Umar ibn al-Khattab reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, ordered us to give charity and at the time I had some wealth. I said to myself, \u201cToday I will outdo Abu Bakr, if ever there were a day to outdo him.\u201d I went with half\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":8243,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/15\/abu-bakr-free-slaves\/","url_meta":{"origin":4031,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Emancipation: Abu Bakr frees slaves he cursed","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 15, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: Abu Bakr once cursed some of his slaves. The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cO Abu Bakr! Those who curse, or those who are true? No, by the Lord of the Ka\u2019bah!\u201d The Prophet said it two or three times. On that day, Abu Bakr\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6719,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/20\/abu-bakr-khalifah-imam-salat\/","url_meta":{"origin":4031,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Khilafah: The Prophet orders Abu Bakr to lead prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 20, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Musa reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, became ill, and when his condition was critical, he said, \u201cTell Abu Bakr to lead the people in prayer.\u201d Aisha said, \u201cHe is a soft-hearted man. He will not be able to lead in your place.\u201d The Prophet said\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abu